data.description: ***NEWLY PRICED TO SELL!*** Welcome to "The Disco House" - A Groovy Desert Oasis in Yucca Valley! Extraordinary 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom retreat nestled in the heart of Yucca Valley, just a stone's throw away from the enchanting Joshua Tree National Park. Boasting 2,076 square feet of pure vintage-inspired charm, this unique property transports you straight back to the funky and fabulous 1970s. This incredible home comes with all financials of previous successful rental periods!  Amazing turn key property! Use as residence, vacation home or rental property! The three bedrooms are a delightful mix of bold patterns, vibrant colors, and plush furnishings. The master bedroom boasts an ensuite bathroom with shower. Backyard is a true desert paradise, complete with a pool, hot tub, and a patio perfect for alfresco dining. As the sun sets over the stunning Joshua Tree landscape, the outdoor disco ball comes to life, casting its shimmering light over your private outdoor dance floor. Don't miss your chance to own a slice of the '70s right here in Yucca Valley.
